\"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read on to find out why the 21-year-old former world No.10 made the huge call.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Emma Raducanu will not feature for Great Britain at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\"}, {\"begin\": 890, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999985725481, \"rank\": 1.4224272786888882e-09, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_Davis_Cup_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's because she does not want to risk further injury problems with the drastic change to the clay surface after such a strong spell on the different, faster grass courts.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am very single minded and I do things my own way and in my own time whenever I want,' Raducanu said of her decision to snub the 2024 Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999958654371, \"rank\": 4.134732092997431e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So not in a diva way, [I am] just prioritising my body and my health because I know if I am fit, I know if I am giving my 100%, I know great things are happening and coming.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just do not think there is any need to put additional stress on my body or any risk, especially with my history.'\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The head of Team GB's Olympic tennis team, Iain Bates, is 'comfortable' with Raducanu's call and added: 'Everyone's aware of her history and the double wrist surgery from last year.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999989219483167, \"rank\": 1.0780506508692818e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1591, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\", \"score\": 0.9999612780037035, \"rank\": 3.8723490795172944e-05, \"text\": \"Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ken_Bates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That [change of surface] places a greater stress on her.'\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Men's singles: Saturday, July 27 - Sunday, August 4  Men's doubles: Saturday, July 27 - Saturday, August 3  Women's singles: Saturday, July 27 - Saturday, August 3  Women's doubles: Saturday, July 27 - Sunday, August 4  Mixed doubles: Monday, July 29 - Friday, August 2  Raducanu endured some mixed results on clay earlier this year, suffering ashocking defeat in Madridto Maria Lourdes Carle before deciding toskip the French Opento focus on grass.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2157, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"score\": 0.9781553361727152, \"rank\": 0.0172929033219114, \"text\": \"Maria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\"}, {\"begin\": 2163, \"end\": 2170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lourdes\", \"score\": 0.9995741241815695, \"rank\": 0.000417517079503244, \"text\": \"Lourdes\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lourdes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lourdes\"}, {\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9484472202369421, \"rank\": 0.04955806954133289, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She does not want to go back to clay in 2024 and is instead focusing on the hard-court season ahead of the final Grand Slam of the year at the US Open in New York, where she's guaranteed a place after climbing back inside the world top 100.\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9993999962214618, \"rank\": 0.0005981763750082042, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be British players in the men's singles, women's singles, men's doubles, women's doubles and mixed doubles.\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2491, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9924362834236107, \"rank\": 0.002769444812060624, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unite